creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
Hi, welcome to the official Spanish River Church app!

A little bit about the app:

This app is designed to keep you up to date on what is going on within our community. Find out about upcoming events, sign up to volunteer, share a prayer request, see what our community has to offer and catch up on the latest blogs, podcasts and sermons.

Check out all kinds of interesting content and share it with friends via Facebook, Twitter, or email.

A little bit about us:

We're a family on mission to love God and love others.

SRC is a multiethnic gathering of people whose lives have been reoriented by God. We are unified because we understand how God's love has been extended to us. Motivated by our experience of God's tremendous love for us, we delight in sharing his love with others. We are discovering what it means to live generously and to enjoy the freedom of following Jesus.

While our facilities and presence in the community have grown over time, we have always maintained that church is so much more than a place you "go to." Rather, it's a people who experience, model, and share the good news of God's love.

For more information about Spanish River Church, please visit:
http://www.spanishriver.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.
